      " cetasikānaṃ vibhājanaṃ karissāmi ahaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "67.Cittānantaramuddiṭṭhā, ye ca cetasikā mayā ye ca cetasikā cittānantaraṃ mayā uddiṭṭhā, ito paraṃ idāni tesaṃ cetasikānaṃ vibhājanaṃ karissāmi ahaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
