        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kasmā panettha mettā ca, upekkhā ca na uddhaṭā ettha"
      },
      " etesu yevāpanakadhammesu, niddhāraṇaṃ, mettā ca upekkhā ca ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "dhammarājena"
      },
      " satthunā ",
