      " sabbe te ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "yevāpanā dhammā"
      },
      " yevāpananāmakā pāḷiyaṃ sarūpena eva. Bandhati snehena etasminti bandhu, ādiccassa bandhu ādiccabandhu, tena ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ādiccabandhunā"
      },
      " buddhena ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "na ca uddhaṭā"
      },
      " na desitā."
    ],
    "innerText": "71.Kasmā yevāpanā dhammā, buddhenādiccabandhunā sabbe te yevāpanā dhammā yevāpananāmakā pāḷiyaṃ sarūpena eva. Bandhati snehena etasminti bandhu, ādiccassa bandhu ādiccabandhu, tena ādiccabandhunā buddhena na ca uddhaṭā na desitā."
  },
  {
