        "innerText": "puññesu"
      },
      "kusalesu niyatā cattāro aniyatā pañca sabbe yevāpanā na ca eva tena munivarena vuttā."
    ],
    "innerText": "Chandādhimokkho muditā manasikāro majjhattatā karuṇā viratittayañca puññesukusalesu niyatā cattāro aniyatā pañca sabbe yevāpanā na ca eva tena munivarena vuttā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "74-80"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kasmā panettha phassova, paṭhamaṃ samudīrito ettha"
      },
      " etesu cetasikesu, jātiniddhāraṇaṃ, phassova paṭhamaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "samudīrito"
      },
      " kathito. Kasmā kāraṇā? ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kira"
      },
      " mayā sutaṃ, ārammaṇe cittassa paṭhamaṃ abhinipātattā phasso paṭhamaṃ samudīrito, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "phusitvā pana phassena"
      },
      " phassena ārammaṇaṃ phusitvā yogino vedanāya ārammaṇaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vedaye,"
      },
      " saññāya ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sañjānāti,"
      },
      " cetanāya ārammaṇaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "cetaye"
      },
      ". ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sahajātānaṃ"
      },
      " cetasikānaṃ phassova ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "idha"
      },
      " imasmiṃ citte mahesinā paṭhamaṃ vutto. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Hi"
      },
      " kasmā kāraṇā? Yasmā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "balavapaccayattā,"
      },
      " tasmā vutto. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Akāraṇamidaṃ sabbaṃ, cittānaṃ tu saheva ca"
      },
      " ‘‘paṭhamābhinipātattā’’ti ca ‘‘balavapaccayattā’’ti ca ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "idaṃ sabbaṃ"
      },
      " vacanaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "akāraṇaṃ"
      },
      " ahetukaṃ ayuttaṃ, kasmā kāraṇā? ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Cittajānaṃ"
      },
      " cittehi sahappavattānaṃ cetasikānaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ekuppādādibhāvena"
      },
      " samānuppādasamānanirodhasamānālambaṇasamānavatthukabhāvena pavattito akāraṇaṃ ayuttaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ayaṃ tu paṭhamuppanno, ayaṃ pacchāti natthidaṃ ayaṃ"
      },
      " dhammo paṭhamuppanno, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ayaṃ"
      },
      " dhammo pacchākāle uppanno iti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "idaṃ"
      },
      " vacanaṃ natthi. Balavapaccayattepi kāraṇaṃ na ca dissati. Desanākkamato ceva paṭhamaṃ samudīrito ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "iccevaṃ"
      },
      " iti evaṃ iti iminā mayā vuttappakārena phassassa paṭhamaṃ samudīritataṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "viññunā"
      },
      " vibhāvinā viññeyyaṃ, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "visesato"
      },
      " visesena aññathā na viññeyyaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Na ca pariyesitabboyaṃ, tasmā pubbāparakkamo"
      },
      " yasmā kāraṇā ayaṃ pubbāparakkamo viññunā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "na ca pariyesitabbo"
      },
      " na gavesitabbo, dhammā eva vacanatthalakkhaṇādīhi ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vijānatā"
      },
      " paṇḍitena pariyesitabbā."
    ],
    "innerText": "74-80.Kasmā panettha phassova, paṭhamaṃ samudīrito ettha etesu cetasikesu, jātiniddhāraṇaṃ, phassova paṭhamaṃ samudīrito kathito. Kasmā kāraṇā? Kira mayā sutaṃ, ārammaṇe cittassa paṭhamaṃ abhinipātattā phasso paṭhamaṃ samudīrito, phusitvā pana phassena phassena ārammaṇaṃ phusitvā yogino vedanāya ārammaṇaṃ vedaye, saññāya sañjānāti, cetanāya ārammaṇaṃ cetaye. Sahajātānaṃ cetasikānaṃ phassova idha imasmiṃ citte mahesinā paṭhamaṃ vutto. Hi kasmā kāraṇā? Yasmā balavapaccayattā, tasmā vutto. Akāraṇamidaṃ sabbaṃ, cittānaṃ tu saheva ca ‘‘paṭhamābhinipātattā’’ti ca ‘‘balavapaccayattā’’ti ca idaṃ sabbaṃ vacanaṃ akāraṇaṃ ahetukaṃ ayuttaṃ, kasmā kāraṇā? Cittajānaṃ cittehi sahappavattānaṃ cetasikānaṃ ekuppādādibhāvena samānuppādasamānanirodhasamānālambaṇasamānavatthukabhāvena pavattito akāraṇaṃ ayuttaṃ. Ayaṃ tu paṭhamuppanno, ayaṃ pacchāti natthidaṃ ayaṃ dhammo paṭhamuppanno, ayaṃ dhammo pacchākāle uppanno iti idaṃ vacanaṃ natthi. Balavapaccayattepi kāraṇaṃ na ca dissati. Desanākkamato ceva paṭhamaṃ samudīrito iccevaṃ iti evaṃ iti iminā mayā vuttappakārena phassassa paṭhamaṃ samudīritataṃ viññunā vibhāvinā viññeyyaṃ, visesato visesena aññathā na viññeyyaṃ. Na ca pariyesitabboyaṃ, tasmā pubbāparakkamo yasmā kāraṇā ayaṃ pubbāparakkamo viññunā na ca pariyesitabbo na gavesitabbo, dhammā eva vacanatthalakkhaṇādīhi vijānatā paṇḍitena pariyesitabbā."
  },
